Comment: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:13.81,ED2,,0,0,0,,ROCKET THRUSTER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.75,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Você se sente sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.54,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Você consegue me ouvir agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:33.09,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Sua mente está tão longe, ainda na Terra
