Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:55.20,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}E eu estou chamando o seu nome de novo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:59.45,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Se você estiver se apegando ao medo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:03.62,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Se eu soubesse que os olhos podem se abrir
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.42,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Deixe a luz entrar
